  "body": "### Description\r\nAs a user, I want the units for `--validators-external-signer-timeout` to be shown when I do `--help` so that I know what number to put there. \r\n\r\nThe default is 1000, and I assume it means milliseconds, but who knows `¯\\_(ツ)_/¯`\r\n\r\n### Acceptance Criteria\r\n* Correct units are shown for `--validators-external-signer-timeout` when I do `teku --help`.\r\n\r\n### Versions (Add all that apply)\r\n* Software version: [`teku --version`]\r\n  - teku/v0.11.0-dev-3949f7e2/linux-x86_64/-privatebuild-openjdk64bitservervm-java-13\r\n",
